* You will need to have Caffe (http://caffe.berkeleyvision.org/) installed in order to use Lucid

    Unpack the tar.gz
    Open a terminal and navigate to the unpacked folder
    Enter the following commands in the terminal and enter your password if prompted:
        
        ./configure
        make
        sudo make install
        
    To run Lucid-GTK simply use the following terminal command:

        lucid-gtk
